<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:07:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于伊朗袭击后“持续的局势”，易捷航空暂停飞往以色列的航班直至十月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-suspends-flights-to-israel-until-oct-due-to-ongoing-situation-after-iran-attack/0000018e-e64e-de97-a5bf-f67e344f0000</link><description>该公司表示，由于以色列局势持续发展，易捷航空决定在夏季剩余时间内暂停飞往特拉维夫的航班，直至 10 月 27 日。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-suspends-flights-to-israel-until-oct-due-to-ongoing-situation-after-iran-attack/0000018e-e64e-de97-a5bf-f67e344f0000</guid></item><item><title>为了对抗伊朗和哈马斯，以色列必须努力建立巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-confront-iran-and-hamas-israel-must-work-towards-a-palestinian-state/0000018e-e229-daaf-afaf-e7fd9b390000</link><description>加沙战争和伊朗袭击都清楚地表明以色列需要巴勒斯坦和地区伙伴。为了确保伊朗和哈马斯无法取得胜利，以色列必须停止拖延两国解决方案的进展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-confront-iran-and-hamas-israel-must-work-towards-a-palestinian-state/0000018e-e229-daaf-afaf-e7fd9b390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须权衡对伊朗针对真主党威胁发起的史无前例的袭击的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-weigh-response-to-irans-unprecedented-attack-against-the-threat-of-hezbollah/0000018e-e366-d071-a5be-e7e678700000</link><description>虽然伊朗的袭击需要以色列做出回应这一基本共识似乎跨越了政治界限，但官员们必须考虑到，如果局势进一步升级，伊朗可能会向其在黎巴嫩的代理人施压，要求其加入战争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-weigh-response-to-irans-unprecedented-attack-against-the-threat-of-hezbollah/0000018e-e366-d071-a5be-e7e678700000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗必须将与以色列的私人战争搁置一边并缓解地区紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/iran-must-put-its-private-war-with-israel-to-one-side-and-lower-regional-tensions/0000018e-e3c2-daaf-afaf-e7f7501f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/iran-must-put-its-private-war-with-israel-to-one-side-and-lower-regional-tensions/0000018e-e3c2-daaf-afaf-e7f7501f0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统：任何损害伊朗利益的行为都将受到严厉回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-live/idf-well-respond-to-iranian-missiles-iaea-worried-israel-could-hit-iran-nuclear-sites/0000018e-e478-de89-afbf-fffc831e0000</link><description>外交部长卡茨：我正在领导针对伊朗的外交攻势 ■ 美国官员预计以色列在伊朗境外对伊朗袭击的反应有限 ■ 以色列援助法案将于本周提交美国众议院投票 ■ 抗议者隔夜封锁运送加沙援助物资的卡车长达 6 小时</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 01:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-live/idf-well-respond-to-iranian-missiles-iaea-worried-israel-could-hit-iran-nuclear-sites/0000018e-e478-de89-afbf-fffc831e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列回应高等法院：我们正在解决加沙地带人道主义援助问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israeך-responds-to-high-court-were-fixing-gaza-strip-humanitarian-aid-problems/0000018e-e31a-d08c-a5af-fb7b7a9d0000</link><description>在人权组织向以色列最高法院请愿增加进入加沙地带的援助物资数量后，以色列政府辩称哈马斯和抢劫事件正在扰乱援助物资的分配</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 19:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israeך-responds-to-high-court-were-fixing-gaza-strip-humanitarian-aid-problems/0000018e-e31a-d08c-a5af-fb7b7a9d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙问题上犯了错误。它对伊朗的损失更大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.highlight/israel-made-mistakes-on-gaza-it-has-more-to-lose-on-iran/0000018e-e2c7-d3b0-a1af-faefcf700000</link><description>10月7日和4月13日，以色列遭受袭击。这两次，该国领导层都未能正确评估敌人的意图，而以色列两次都赢得了西方世界的同情——但这并没有持续太久。内塔尼亚胡再次误判的代价要高得多</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 18:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.highlight/israel-made-mistakes-on-gaza-it-has-more-to-lose-on-iran/0000018e-e2c7-d3b0-a1af-faefcf700000</guid></item><item><title>国际压力加大，以色列战时内阁考虑应对伊朗袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-mulls-response-to-iran-attack-amid-rising-international-pressure/0000018e-e2e6-d08c-a5af-faff82780000</link><description>一位熟悉战时内阁审议情况的消息人士称，以色列国防机构正在敦促对伊朗采取军事回应，但在美国的压力下，机会之窗将在几天内关闭</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 18:20:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-mulls-response-to-iran-attack-amid-rising-international-pressure/0000018e-e2e6-d08c-a5af-faff82780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 192 天：哈马斯提出基于 41 天休战的提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-192-hamas-presents-proposal-based-on-41-day-truce/0000018e-e2a9-de89-afbf-ffad8e2f0001</link><description>据报道，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡办公室的官员表示，“以色列不能允许如此大规模的袭击”而不做出某种回应。 ■ 哈马斯向调解员发出了围绕 41 天停火的建议。联合国表示，真主党声称对以色列-黎巴嫩边境四名以色列国防军士兵受伤的爆炸事件负责。在战争结束 192 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:53:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-192-hamas-presents-proposal-based-on-41-day-truce/0000018e-e2a9-de89-afbf-ffad8e2f0001</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击后，由于安全局势，易捷航空取消飞往以色列的航班一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-cancels-flights-to-israel-for-a-week-due-to-security-situation-after-irans-attack/0000018e-e251-d9ed-a9ce-fed79da30000</link><description>这家英国廉价航空公司宣布，预计 4 月 21 日（逾越节前一天）之前不会恢复往返以色列的航班</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-cancels-flights-to-israel-for-a-week-due-to-security-situation-after-irans-attack/0000018e-e251-d9ed-a9ce-fed79da30000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击后，拜登为内塔尼亚胡提供了另一条生命线，但以色列右翼基地不会接受</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-right-wing-base-wont-let-netanyahu-take-bidens-lifeline-after-the-iran-attack/0000018e-e1ef-d9f8-a7df-e1ff06d40000</link><description>导致哈马斯 10 月 7 日发动袭击的原因正是导致伊朗在周日发射数百枚导弹和无人机的原因：人们认为内塔尼亚胡右翼政府领导下的以色列软弱、分裂，并且与美国关系不好。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-right-wing-base-wont-let-netanyahu-take-bidens-lifeline-after-the-iran-attack/0000018e-e1ef-d9f8-a7df-e1ff06d40000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击的后果是结束以色列各条战线战争的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/the-aftermath-of-irans-attack-is-an-opportunity-to-end-israels-wars-on-all-fronts/0000018e-e124-de2f-a5ff-e93eee6d0000</link><description>伊朗明确表示，如果以色列不回应，本轮谈判就结束。希望以色列领导人不会被拖入危险的升级之中</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:12:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/the-aftermath-of-irans-attack-is-an-opportunity-to-end-israels-wars-on-all-fronts/0000018e-e124-de2f-a5ff-e93eee6d0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党称其在黎巴嫩和以色列边境附近放置了一枚炸弹，造成四名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-says-it-planted-a-bomb-on-lebanon-israel-border-wounding-four-idf-soldiers/0000018e-e1ea-d9df-abdf-e7eb72370000</link><description>以色列军队称爆炸发生在黎巴嫩领土数百米处 ■ 以色列国防军称爆炸来源不明，真主党声称对此负责</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 14:28:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-says-it-planted-a-bomb-on-lebanon-israel-border-wounding-four-idf-soldiers/0000018e-e1ea-d9df-abdf-e7eb72370000</guid></item><item><title>抵制“战争的狂喜”：宗教左翼以色列士兵眼中的加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/resisting-the-ecstasy-of-war-gaza-through-the-eyes-of-religious-leftist-israeli-soldiers/0000018e-ce86-d283-a5ee-fe9ff47e0000</link><description>对于宗教左翼分子来说，他们在加沙担任预备役军人期间，围绕军事命令的道德复杂性在他们内部引发了一场独特的战斗——尤其是在目睹与犹太价值观相悖的“可耻行为”时</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/resisting-the-ecstasy-of-war-gaza-through-the-eyes-of-religious-leftist-israeli-soldiers/0000018e-ce86-d283-a5ee-fe9ff47e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯坚持与伊朗结盟对抗以色列，但承认自己在加沙战争中是孤立的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-clings-to-its-alliance-with-iran-but-acknowledges-it-stands-alone-in-the-gaza-war/0000018e-e134-d09b-afff-ef3ded730000</link><description>哈马斯的加沙领导层完全支持伊朗对以色列的袭击，但它也明白，德黑兰几乎不可能采取类似的行动来帮助该组织实现其野心并确保其在战后加沙地带的地位</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:45:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-clings-to-its-alliance-with-iran-but-acknowledges-it-stands-alone-in-the-gaza-war/0000018e-e134-d09b-afff-ef3ded730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将加沙的一位奶奶与家人分开。她的死将困扰她的子孙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-troops-separated-a-gaza-grandma-from-her-family-her-death-will-haunt-her-descendants/0000018e-e154-dba1-a7df-eb5f1f900000</link><description>以色列士兵射杀了加沙奶奶吗？她是死于饥饿还是口渴，卧床不起，孤身一人吗？她是被浓烟窒息还是被烧死的？</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-troops-separated-a-gaza-grandma-from-her-family-her-death-will-haunt-her-descendants/0000018e-e154-dba1-a7df-eb5f1f900000</guid></item><item><title>联合国：以色列加沙缓冲区几乎所有建筑物被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/un-almost-all-buildings-in-israels-buffer-zone-in-gaza-were-destroyed/0000018e-e12a-d09b-afff-ef2f2ccf0000</link><description>据联合国卫星中心称，缓冲区内 90% 的建筑物遭到损坏或摧毁。国际社会认为该项目毁坏了数千座建筑物，可能构成战争罪</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/un-almost-all-buildings-in-israels-buffer-zone-in-gaza-were-destroyed/0000018e-e12a-d09b-afff-ef2f2ccf0000</guid></item><item><title>“隐藏面粉”：以色列阿拉伯人如何面对伊朗的袭击而大笑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hide-the-flour-how-palestinians-in-israel-laughed-in-the-face-of-irans-attack/0000018e-e12f-d09b-afff-ef2f28110000</link><description>当导弹、火箭和无人机从伊朗飞向以色列时，一些巴勒斯坦人爬上屋顶记录这一事件，而另一些人则通过社交媒体并用幽默作为应对机制</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hide-the-flour-how-palestinians-in-israel-laughed-in-the-face-of-irans-attack/0000018e-e12f-d09b-afff-ef2f28110000</guid></item><item><title>美国报道：伊朗一半弹道导弹失败，以色列空军基地飞机受损；阿联酋与沙特分享情报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/u-s-sources-half-of-iranian-ballistic-missiles-failed-idf-aircraft-damaged/0000018e-e0d0-d7e5-a1fe-e7d1bf3a0000</link><description>美国官员告诉美国广播公司新闻和华尔街日报，五枚弹道导弹击中了南部的内瓦蒂姆空军基地，损坏了一架运输机，四枚弹道导弹击中了另一个基地。在美国压力下，阿联酋和沙特阿拉伯在袭击前分享了伊朗的袭击计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:38:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/u-s-sources-half-of-iranian-ballistic-missiles-failed-idf-aircraft-damaged/0000018e-e0d0-d7e5-a1fe-e7d1bf3a0000</guid></item><item><title>勇敢对抗伊朗的阿拉伯国家不会参与协助以色列的反击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-stood-up-to-iran-wont-be-on-board-to-assist-an-israeli-counterstrike/0000018e-e0df-d4da-a18f-ecfffe8e0000</link><description>约旦、沙特阿拉伯和该地区其他国家都在与美国甚至以色列结盟，以平衡其内部稳定。以色列打击伊朗的前景可能会阻止他们与伊朗结盟</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-stood-up-to-iran-wont-be-on-board-to-assist-an-israeli-counterstrike/0000018e-e0df-d4da-a18f-ecfffe8e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>